{"tid":1126333,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"（劇透）Endgame致敬位","createTime":"2019-04-26T10:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T11:05:21.000Z","uid":188418,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0395b1683aaab146b3f909206977127967957595","tid":1126333,"uid":188418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:16:58.000Z","msg":"Hulk撻完手指救人之後<br />\nThanos嚟地球突襲轟炸Avengers總部<br />\n算唔算係向Mandarin致敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTony經歷兩次畀人突襲住所<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8470f8427097b19560ab50dc92b2600801a0e7c2","tid":1126333,"uid":188418,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"有幸出生喺呢個年代 90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經歷哂哈利波特八集同呢二十二齣Marvel電影<br />\n兩個經典系列<br />\n<br />\n大個一定要畀個仔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfd66999ad1404e3d5ff20f62255996a0c652b9","tid":1126333,"uid":208809,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:29:30.000Z","msg":"仲有魔戒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3827a3c5627014946a5806295149eaf9e9b3e169","tid":1126333,"uid":57914,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:32:57.000Z","msg":"亞凡達<br />\nNolan<br />\n<br />\n仲有各種電視劇GoT, Doctor Who"},{"pid":"389c699cf97771562a75a931969485b322f434fc","tid":1126333,"uid":188418,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3827a3c5627014946a5806295149eaf9e9b3e169","tid":1126333,"uid":57914,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:32:57.000Z","msg":"亞凡達<br />\nNolan<br />\n<br />\n仲有各種電視劇GoT, Doctor Who"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:02:36.000Z","msg":"Nolan嗰啲當然 Memento, Inception, The Prestige, Interstellar, The Dark Knight Trilogy, Dunkirk齣齣經典<br />\n但都唔算係一系列<br />\n當然僅次重有Star Wars同James Bond<br />\n但我個人麻麻地星球大戰<br />\n而占士邦太重英倫風 型係型 睇係好睇<br />\n但唔會有咁多忠實粉絲<br />\n同埋都唔算只係誕生喺90後00後嘅年代<br />\n<br />\n而哈利波特同Marvel系列都尚算完整 唔爛尾 觀眾粉絲全世界咁多 相信有大部分都滿意 相反Fast &amp; Furious系列頭四五集都幾好 但走下坡 最近Hobbs同Shaw嗰齣我都唔識形容喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重有阿凡達2等到蚊瞓<br />\n要等第三集 占士金馬倫都唔知賣咗鹹鴨蛋未<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我認同電視劇好多都經典 但電影嘅話呢兩個系列無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c099dab25804fcadc2b737026d9e7498e20b7ef7","tid":1126333,"uid":188418,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9bfd66999ad1404e3d5ff20f62255996a0c652b9","tid":1126333,"uid":208809,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:29:30.000Z","msg":"仲有魔戒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:05:21.000Z","msg":"三部曲嘅經典實在太多<br />\n再多啲嘅得星球大戰, DC系列, Fast &amp; Furious, Jurassic Park<br />\n但都唔夠哈利波特同Marvel系列撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}